raw_text = "~ start
## 3pm
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Jessica: Listen up cubs
Jessica: This Friday's the meet and greet with this Fall's new batch
Jessica: The freshest crop of pussy arrives every September
Jason: LETS GOOO
Jason: Been waiting for something this week since my club's down
Nina: Down boy 🙄
Jessica: Just one catch, each group gets only one early access ticket
Jason: FUCK!! That sucks (Can it be me?)
Player: 😅
Jessica: Poor Alex though
Jessica: The only boy on the football team without a dorm wife of his own
Jessica: It's almost sad. I genuinely pity you
Alex: Don't
Alex: I don't really give a shit, the girls line up after my games anyway
Alex: And I have someone I'm gonna hook up with soon heh
Jessica: We'll see
Jessica: What about the last cub? Not curious at all?
Player: I am... I guess getting the ticket isn't going to be easy
Jessica: Cub of such little faith
Jessica: I am the most curious about you, don't disappoint me
Jessica: All you need is a little luck
Jessica: With the dice function on your phones, we'll decide based on highest number
Erika: Oh no, a numbers thing again? 😣
Nina: Boring af
Nina: Why not have the highest roll pick who goes?
Jessica: I don't hate that idea
Jessica: Fine
Jessica: If you win, you pick another cub to go
Erika: Spicy, I like it
if Story.has_flag(\"Erika1\"):
	Erika: Hope my boy wins 😉💛
	Player: Thanks 😅
	Nina: Your boy? Really? 🙄
Jessica: Hurry up and roll
Jason: Watch and learn boys
System: Jason has rolled 2.
Jason: ...is that good?
Jason: Ngl I don't really get how this works 😅
Nina: LMAOOO
Nina: It's a 2 you dumb horny dick, I guess you're safe
Jason: That's totally me
Nina: Dick first, thinking never?
Jason: You wanna give it a ride?
Jason: Shooting my shot 🙏
Nina: EWW. HARD pass 🖕
Jessica: Alright break it up, next roll
- [Roll]
	System: You have rolled 4.
Nina: A four??
Nina: Couldn't squeeze out the 6 huh? Fuck
Nina: If Alex beats you I'm gonna lose it
System: Alex has rolled 3.
Alex: 3
if Story.has_flag(\"Nina1\"):
	Nina: HAHAHA, guess who isn't going
- [...]
	Player: ...
- We're still scheduled for that date [if Story.has_flag(\"Nina1\")]
	Player: We're still scheduled for that date
	Nina: 🖕🖕🖕
Jessica: Well. The new cub takes it
Jessica: You get to choose who goes this Friday
Jessica: So who's it going to be
if Story.has_flag(\"Nina1\"):
	Nina: Who indeed HAHA
Jessica: Jason or Alex?
Player: I don't really know if this matters much to me but...
- Jason
	set Story.flag = \"DHJason\"
	Player: Jason can have it
	Jason: AYY my guy 🙌 Returning the favor huh?
	Player: Sure thing!
	Jason: Wait hold on, this is the dorm wife deal right?
	Jason: Eh... idk man that's a whole lot
	Jason: I'm more of a play around and move on kinda guy
	Jason: The locked-down commitment thing really ain't me
	Jessica: You'll change your tune soon enough
	Jessica: They always do
	Jason: Lol we'll see I guess
	Jason: You got any down-bad bimbos?
	Jason: Y'know like super sluts?
	Jessica: Honey, I don't think you understand that you get to shape the girl to your every desire
	Jessica: All expenses are covered by the Sorority
	Jason: Sweet really? Like I get to pick any girl I want and MAKE her the way I want her to be?
	Jessica: Now you're getting it
	Jason: 🤩
	Jason: Daddys hyped for first pick
- Alex
	set Story.flag = \"DHAlex\"
	Player: Alex can have it I guess
	Alex: Good choice kid
	Alex: About time the damn Sorority gave me my prize
	Alex: Though my expectations are low seeing what I see here
	Jessica: And here I am, wasting my pity on you
	Alex: I don't need your pity lady
	Jessica: Watch it, I heard a bit about you from your captain
	Jessica: Any signs of hurting the girls and you're out
	Jessica: I hear you're on your last strike from expulsion too
	Alex: Yeah yeah... that shit doesn't bother me
	Alex: But you don't have to worry
	Alex: I'll be gentle
	Jessica: You better, I'll be watching you
	Alex: Gonna need a girl that lets me do whatever I want to her
	Jessica: Oh honey, every man finds what they're looking for in the Sorority
	Alex: Sweet
Jessica: Then it's settled
- [continue]
Jessica: Don't embarrass the house this Friday
Nina: and try not to drool all over the merchandise 🙄
Nina: We worked hard rounding these girls up
if Story.has_flag(\"DHJason\"):
	Jason: You got it
	Jessica: The new batch is a bit \"inexperienced\" lets say
	Jessica: All the better to shape them for personal use
	Jessica: You might have to give them a little push though...
	Jessica: Or maybe a big one
	Jessica: But if ANY girl complains about you, your ass is thrown out and membership revoked
	Jason: Leave it to me your queen-ness 🫡
	Jason: I know how to handle fragile goods
	Jason: I can be real convincing 😝
if Story.has_flag(\"DHAlex\"):
	Alex: Do I look like the embarrassing kind?
	Jessica: The new batch is a bit \"inexperienced\" lets say
	Jessica: All the better to shape them for personal use
	Jessica: You might have to give them a little push though...
	Jessica: Or maybe a big one
	Alex: Sweet
	Jessica: But if ANY girl complains about you, your ass is thrown out and membership revoked
	Alex: I always get what I want
	Alex: And nobody ever complains
Jessica: For the rest of the group
Jessica: The next one will be open to all members so don't cry about it yet, you'll get your slut
if Story.has_flag(\"Erika1\"):
	Erika: I'm glad my date is gonna be there eventually 😘
	Player: I will?
	Erika: It's open invite sweetheart
	Erika: And you wouldn't let the hounds come for lil old Erika would you? 🥺
	Nina: Fuck this, I'm out
	Player: 😆
if Story.has_flag(\"Nina1\"):
	Erika: Mhmm.
	Erika: You and Nina can finally be together 🥰
	Nina: 🤢🤮🤮🤮
	Player: 😆
Jessica: Check DMs Erika, I got some stuff for you
Erika: Yes queeen! 🥰
Jessica: Alright, begone the rest of you hoes
Jessica: I've got things to do
if Story.has_flag(\"DHJason\"):
	do social_post(\"jason_meetgreet\")
=> END
"
